desc: Lulu Liquor Cakes is a Knoxville-based cake shop that provides gourmet, alcohol-infused cakes and cakes jars to East Tennessee and surrounding areas. Served in prepackaged jars, they're perfect for birthday gifts, party favors, bridesmaid presents, and more!

layout.text: All The Boozy Goodness In A Jar!
Providing Gourmet, Alcohol-Infused Cakes & Cake Jars
